Comment: 1,0:02:37.01,0:02:40.85,Main,from_ocr,0,0,0,,TẬP 7\NNỮ HOÀNG HEAVY METAL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{VT! Your shift's up?}VT! Chị nghỉ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{Finally. How about you?}Cuối cùng cũng đến giờ nghỉ. Còn anh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:57.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm off to Europa now.}Tôi tính đến Europa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.55,Main,split,0,0,0,,{That's got pretty good pay.}Lương cao đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.99,Main,split,0,0,0,,{It's nothing compared to yours.}Không bì được với chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:03.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{I heard you made a round-trip\Nfrom here to Venus in 4 days?}Nghe nói chị đã đi một vòng\Ntừ đây tới Sao Kim trong bốn ngày?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{Three days.}Ba ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.11,Main,split,0,0,0,,{See what I mean?}Tôi tính nói thế đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:09.03,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Anyway, take it easy.}Dù sao cũng từ từ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:11.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah, I forgot.}À, tôi quên mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:13.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{VT!}VT!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{You're still not giving up?}Anh vẫn chưa từ bỏ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:21.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{Of course not! How much\Ndo ya think I lent ya?}Tất nhiên là không!\NLần này chị nghĩ tôi cược bao nhiêu tiền?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:23.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{Suit yourself...}Tùy anh thôi, sao cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:29.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{All right. You only get one shot,\Nand you get no clues.}Anh biết thỏa thuận mà.\NChỉ có một cơ hội, không gợi ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:32.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! VT, your name is...}Được rồi! VT, tên chị là...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.22,0:03:34.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{Vivian Tillana.}Vivian Tillana.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{Nope!}Sai rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:38.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, man...}Ôi trời!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:40.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{This is a bad omen...}Thật là điềm xấu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:42.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{You be careful now.}Từ giờ cẩn thận nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:48.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, you know that Cock-Eye guy that\Nwas worth 8 million the other day?}Biết khoản tiền thưởng tám triệu\Nhôm trước chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{Believe it or not,\NI was the one who caught him!}Tin hay không thì tùy,\Ntôi là người đã bắt được Cookwife!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:54.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean, the other day?\NThat was 10 years ago, you old geezer!}Hôm đó là hôm nào?\NChuyện mười năm trước rồi, lão già!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:04:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{What are you saying, you young'uns!\NI was the one that taught Telpsicorei!}Đám trẻ ranh các cậu thì biết gì!\NTôi là người đã huấn luyện Telpsicorei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{You mean the legendary bounty hunter?}Tay săn tiền thưởng huyền thoại à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:06.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{Every bounty cowered in fear just\Nat the mention of his name.}Đúng vậy. Nghe nhắc đến tên anh ta,\Nlà đám bị truy lùng co vòi sợ hãi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.46,0:04:08.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, everyone knows that.}Ai cũng biết mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Zeros.}Chào Zeros.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{Welcome, VT. The usual?}Chào VT. Như thường lệ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:27.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{What's going on today?\NThe place is usually empty.}Hôm nay có chuyện gì vậy?\NNơi này thường vắng teo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:32.57,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Oh, this?}À, {Apparently a bounty named Decker\Nis gonna pass by around here.}tin đồn là có một gã tên Decker đi qua đây,\Nvà cái đầu hắn được treo giải thưởng.
Comment: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.80,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Oh, this?}À.
Comment: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:32.57,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Apparently a bounty named Decker\Nis gonna pass by around here.}Tin đồn là có một gã tên Decker đi qua đây,\Nvà cái đầu hắn được treo giải thưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{They're all bounty hunters.}Họ đều là thợ săn tiền thưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:39.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{No wonder they all look so cheap.}Thảo nào mặt ai trông cũng rẻ tiền hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{What was that about\N"top secret" information? [letting bleed to lower CPS]}Còn nguồn tin tuyệt mật đó thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:44.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{This place is full of our kind. [1 less frame lead-in]}Nơi này đầy bọn săn tiền thưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{And I got a hangover today, too...}Tôi xỉn và thấy muốn bệnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:52.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{Besides, we don't know the face.\NThe only clue is a dragon-shaped tattoo.}Ta còn không biết mặt hắn ta\Nchỉ biết hắn có hình xăm rồng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:54.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{Faye?}Faye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:58.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{Like that place is gonna be any better.}{\i1}Như thể cô ấy sẽ gặp may ở nơi đó.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:00.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Welcome to Woody's!}{\i0}{\i1}Chào mừng đến Woody's!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:04.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{are celebrating their birthdays}{\i0}{\i1}Ngay bây giờ,{\i0}\N{\i1}tất cả những bạn nhỏ có sinh nhật hôm nay{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:07.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{with Mackey and Mannie!}{\i0}{\i1}đều có thể chụp ảnh cùng Mackey và Mannie!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.12,0:05:10.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{ [9 frames]}{\i0}{\i1}Các vị phụ huynh hãy đến gặp phục vụ!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:19.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hi.}Chào.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:23.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{Whadduyawant? Ya wanna get some?}Muốn gì? Làm vài nháy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:26.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'd rather be the one that gives some.}Nếu phải chọn, tôi thích là người ở trên.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm fine with that. [end just before the gun or do normal lead-out?]}Được thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:30.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hands in the air, Decker!}Giơ tay lên, Decker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:35.69,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Don't be so difficult! [3 frames extra lead-in or just snap to start keyframe?]}Tôi sẽ gặp rắc rối!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:37.95,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Just get the hell over here.}Bình tĩnh. Qua đây nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:39.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{But I have work!}Không, tôi phải làm việc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{Just make yourself comfortable!}Hãy thoải mái!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:42.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{Git!}Lại đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{P-Please, stop.}Xin anh, đừng mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'll give you a good time.}Anh sẽ cho cô em thỏa mãn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{Stop!}Dừng đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:49.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{Someone!}Ai đó giúp với!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:51.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{What the hell are ya?!}Cái quái gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{VT!}VT!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{So it's a bounty hunter's job to chase\Na woman's ass instead of a bounty?}Từ khi nào việc của thợ săn tiền thưởng\Nlại là săn đuổi phụ nữ thay vì tiền?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:03.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{Sorry, but this is my job.}Xin lỗi, nhưng đây là việc của chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.14,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Wh-What—}Cái gì—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.30,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Don't play dumb with me.}Đừng giả ngu với chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{That dragon-shaped tattoo\Nis unmistakable proof. [9 frames]}Hình xăm rồng đó\Nlà tất cả bằng chứng chị cần.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{Y-You got the wrong man.}Bắt nhầm người rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, you over there!}Này, anh kia!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:15.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{Call the police!}Gọi cảnh sát đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:17.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{Tell them I caught Decker the bounty!}Nói với họ là tôi bắt được Decker rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:34.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{This is...?}Cái này...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yakkun, the eight-eyed eel.}Là con lươn tám mắt, Yakkun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{Don't be so mistakable!}Nhầm lẫn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{Why you!}Sao mụ dám...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:15.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{You!}Đồ khốn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{VT!}VT!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,{You're wearing my patience thin.}Mụ tưởng mụ ngon à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:27.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What the hell are ya?}Mày bị cái quái gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:30.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{Grudges over lost food aren't a pretty sight!}Quậy đồ ăn của tao thì tao không để yên.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:34.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{Shit, let's get this guy too!}Chết tiệt, xử cả thằng này nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{Found him! [9 frames]}Thấy ngươi rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:14.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{Shit, I'll get you back for this!}Chết tiệt, bọn tao sẽ nhớ vụ này!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.88,0:08:17.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{Uh, just kidding.}Đùa thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:19.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{Forget about us!}Đừng nhớ tụi em nha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{My 12 million...}Mười hai triệu của mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:37.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{Really. Bounty hunters are all stupid scum.}Trời ạ, bọn thợ săn tiền thưởng\Ntoàn là những kẻ ngu ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.38,Main,split,0,0,0,,{You think so?}Chị nghĩ vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.42,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Ừ!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:43.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{As far as I know, they're all\Nliving their lives by gambling.}Theo như tôi biết, họ đều là những kẻ\Nđánh cược cả cuộc đời mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{Well, maybe so.}Ừ, có lẽ vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:49.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{Come over here. I'll treat you to a drink.}Lại đây. Tôi sẽ mời cậu một ly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:58.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{What? Bean sprouts are good for you!}Gì chứ? Ăn giá rất tốt cho mày!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:04.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{Give me a break! That's all we have!}Thôi đi chứ! Ta chỉ còn nhiêu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:05.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh! Here it comes!}Ôi! Đây rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:08.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, it's you, Faye. That was quick.}Ồ, là cô à, Faye. Nhanh thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:11.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{What?!}Gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:14.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{But that sure is a disgusting drink.}Dù gì thì nó vẫn là thứ đồ uống kinh tởm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.34,Main,split,0,0,0,,{It's a prairie oyster.}Prairie oyster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.70,Main,split,0,0,0,,{It's good for hangovers.}Giã rượu rất tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:26.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{You're the second person I've\Nmet that drinks that stuff.}Cậu là người thứ hai tôi từng gặp\Nchịu uống thứ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:27.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{And the first one?}Người đầu tiên là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{My husband.}Chồng tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{VT!}VT!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.35,Main,split,0,0,0,,{We'll get it this time.}Lần này sẽ đoán được.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:34.97,Main,split,0,0,0,,{The money!}Tiền đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:37.18,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Once for the three of you?}Một lần đoán cho ba người các ông à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:38.39,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Ừ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{Suit yourself.}Tùy thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{All right! Here we go!}Được rồi! Bắt đầu nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:47.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{VT, your name is...}VT, tên của cô là...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:49.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{I think Adrienne is good.}Tôi nghĩ tên Adrienne có vẻ đúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{That doesn't start with a V.}Đâu có bắt đầu với từ V.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:56.66,Main,split,0,0,0,,{That's why I said we should\Nstick with Leticia!}Nên mới nói tập trung vào tên Leticia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:57.44,Main,split,0,0,0,,{You think so?}Ông nghĩ vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:10:00.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{I can have that money if\NI guess your name?}Ai đoán được tên chị\Nthì được số tiền đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:02.00,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.99,Main,split,0,0,0,,{I don't remember who started it,}Tôi quên ai đã khơi mào trò này,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:07.33,Main,,0,0,0,,{but it kept piling up,\Nand here we are now.}nhưng tôi thắng cả cọc tiền\Nnhư cậu thấy đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:09.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{Can I try too?}Tôi thử được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Spike! It's me!}{\i0}{\i1}Spike! Là tôi đây!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.43,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Faye let Decker get away!}{\i0}Nhỏ Faye chết tiệt để Decker thoát rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:15.66,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Go after him now—}{\i0}Đuổi theo hắn đi—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{Spike!}Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:23.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{Get lost!}Biến đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:26.43,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Idiotic lying scum! [8 frames if you want to start on that low "mmm" sound]}Đồ đần, tồi tệ, dối trá!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.85,Main,split,0,0,0,,{I ain't treating you!}Tôi không trả tiền nước cho cậu đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{No, Spike!}Không, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, my.}Ôi trời.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, this, those whachamacallit brothers\Ndid this before they took off.}Ừ, là mấy gã đó làm trước khi bỏ đi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{And you were watching?}Cô đã thấy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.45,0:10:48.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{Uh-huh.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,{Why didn't you tell me?}Sao không cho tôi biết?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:55.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{What? I just told you right now!}Gì cơ? Tôi vừa mới nói đó thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:03.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{What?}Gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:12.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, VT... going home?}VT, về nhà à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:14.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{Got a problem with that? Come on, Zeros.}Có vấn đề gì à? Đi nào, Zeros.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:21.87,Main,split,0,0,0,,{ doing?}{\i0}Cậu đang làm gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.18,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Hitchhiking.}Xin quá giang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{My machine was vandalized.}Tàu của tôi đã bị phá hoại.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:29.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{You're really a stupid...}Đúng là đồ đần...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:32.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{...lying, shameless scum of a bounty hunter?}Tay săn tiền thưởng dối trá,\Nvớ vẩn không biết xấu hổ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:34.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{If you don't stop with all this...!}Nếu cậu không thôi đi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{Follow me.}Theo tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:47.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{Can I bring someone with me?}Mang theo một người được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:57.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{Man! How many times do I\Nhave to say the same thing?!}{\i1}Trời ơi!{\i0}\N{\i1}Phải lặp lại bao nhiêu lần nữa đây.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:00.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{He was short, bald, wearing\Nglasses, and a sarasvati...}Hắn thấp, hói, đeo kính,\Nvà có hình Thất Phúc Thần...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:02.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{Huh?! What?!}Hả? Nói gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:03.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{I just said...}Tôi vừa nói...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:07.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Really! Can you turn that\Nshit-loud noise off?!}Trời ạ!\NTắt cái thứ tào lao ầm ĩ này được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{They say, "When in Rome,\Ndo as the Romans do."}Có nghe câu "Nhập gia tùy tục" chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:15.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{And it's not shit-loud noise.}Và nó không phải thứ tào lao ầm ĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:17.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's called heavy metal!}Nó gọi là rock heavy metal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:32.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{Really, both of you together...}Thiệt tình chứ, cả hai người bọn họ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:35.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{Who do you think is going to repair these?}Họ nghĩ ai sẽ sửa cái này chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{What the hell am I supposed to do\Nwith that little bit of information?}Tôi phải làm gì\Nvới cái mớ thông tin cỏn con đó?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:44.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{How many bald people with glasses do\Nyou think there are in this universe?}Cô nghĩ vũ trụ này\Ncó bao nhiêu gã hói đeo kính?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:47.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{So I said, bald, short, with glasses,}Tôi nói rồi, hói, lùn, đeo kính...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:51.62,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{and driving a gaudy truck\Nwith Sarasvati painted on it!}và lái một chiếc xe tải lòe loẹt\Ncó hình Thất Phúc Thần.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah?}{\i1}A lô?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:56.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That you, VT?}{\i0}{\i1}Là chị à VT?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.76,0:12:58.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, Otto. What's up?}{\i1}Ôi, Otto. Sao thế?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I got into a hit-and-run.}{\i0}{\i1}Có kẻ tông trúng tôi rồi bỏ chạy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:01.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Gì cơ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:05.18,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The guy cut in line at the gate entrance,\Nrammed me, and took off!}{\i0}{\i1}Có một gã chen hàng ở cổng vào,{\i0}\N{\i1}tông trúng tôi rồi bỏ chạy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:09.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Shit, I gotta make him pay for repairs!}{\i0}{\i1}Chết tiệt,{\i0}\N{\i1}tôi phải bắt hắn trả tiền sửa tàu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Tell me if you see him!}{\i0}{\i1}Thấy hắn thì báo tôi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Anything specific?}{\i0}{\i1}Có nhận dạng gì đặc biệt không?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:13.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{Let's see...}Xem nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:17.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{There was some oriental goddess drawn on...}Có vẽ hình một nữ thần châu Á trên...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:20.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Wait a minute! Was it Sarasvati?}{\i0}{\i1}Chờ một chút! Là Thất Phúc Thần à?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:23.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah, her. How'd you know?}Phải, đúng rồi. Sao chị biết?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{Zeros.}Zeros.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:30.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Breaker one nine, Breaker one nine.}{\i0}{\i1}Gọi kênh 19.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.72,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{To all truckers in the asteroid belt.}{\i0}Tài xế ở các tiểu hành tinh chú ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.86,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This is Heavy Metal Queen.}{\i0}Nữ Hoàng Heavy Metal đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:37.46,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{with Sarasvati painted on it. Thanks.}{\i0}Nếu thấy chiếc xe tải lòe loẹt\N có hình Thất Phúc Thần,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{with Sarasvati painted on it. Thanks.}{\i0}hãy liên hệ với tôi ngay. Cảm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:42.52,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{VT, this is Love Machine.}{\i0}VT, Cỗ Máy Tình Yêu đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:45.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What's up with it? Some guy\Nyou were chasing ran away?}{\i0}{\i1}Có chuyện gì thế?{\i0}\N{\i1}Chị đang săn lùng kẻ nào à?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Something like that.}{\i0}{\i1}Ừ, đại loại thế.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:50.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{I haven't seen the guy,\Nbut I'll be on the lookout.}Tôi chưa thấy gì, nhưng tôi sẽ để ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Thanks. It'll help.}{\i0}{\i1}Cảm ơn. Tôi rất cảm kích.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:56.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{This is Sneaky Snake. Did you\Nsay it was a painting of a clown?}Rắn Lươn Lẹo đây. Chị nói\Nhắn mang một cái mặt nạ ngộ nghĩnh à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.94,0:13:57.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Nope.}{\i0}{\i1}Không.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:00.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{This is Spider Mike, Black Panther of Jupiter.}{\i0}{\i1}Mike Nhện đây, Báo Đen của Sao Mộc.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:05.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{VT, I've never met you, but I hear lots of\Nrumors about the Heavy Metal Queen.}{\i0}{\i1}Tôi chưa từng gặp chị, nhưng đã{\i0}\N{\i1}nghe danh tiếng của Nữ Hoàng Heavy Metal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:08.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{Thanks for the compliment. So, any info?}Cảm ơn anh! Vậy có thông tin gì không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:11.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{I passed by someone like the one you're\Nlooking for about 10 minutes ago. [9 frames]}Khoảng mười phút trước,\Ntôi chạy ngang qua một gã trông giống thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{It was around the Linus mines.}Nó ở quanh khu mỏ Linus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:15.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That help?}{\i0}{\i1}Có ích không?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{Thanks, I'll owe you one.}Cảm ơn, tôi nợ anh đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:29.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{I gotta exchange this too...}Trời ơi, có vẻ phải thay cái này.
Comment: 1,0:14:29.06,0:14:33.02,Main,from_ocr,0,0,0,,MỎ LINUS
Comment: 1,0:14:29.06,0:14:33.02,Main,from_ocr,0,0,0,,NGUY HIỂM\NTRÁNH XA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:43.36,Main,,0,0,0,,{There he is!}Hắn kia rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:55.24,Main,,0,0,0,,{Trying to throw me off his trail...}Cố chạy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:59.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{Maybe in the next century!}Còn lâu mới thoát nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:14.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, is the stupid, lying, shameless\Nscum of a bounty hunter around?}Gã thợ săn tiền thưởng ngu ngốc, dối trá,\Nvớ vẩn không biết xấu hổ phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.60,Main,,0,0,0,,{What?! The Linus mines?! [9 frames]}Chị nói là mỏ Linus à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.68,Main,split,0,0,0,,{You're being reckless!}Thật điên mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.34,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What did you say?}{\i0}Cậu nói gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:20.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{Stay away from Decker!}Tránh xa Decker ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:23.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{His cargo is dangerous!}Hắn đang chở thứ nguy hiểm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:23.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:31.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{Wait! I called first dibs on Decker!}Khoan!\NLà tôi phát hiện ra Decker trước nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:41.27,Main,split,0,0,0,,{What is this? Really?}Cái gì đây? Thiệt đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.83,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Do I have to put this silly thing on?}Anh gắn cái thứ ngu ngốc đó vào à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:46.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{I would have preferred that it was\Nyour loud mouth that broke.}Ước gì cái thứ bị hư\Nlà cái miệng to mồm của cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:47.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{I heard that.}Tôi nghe đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:49.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm going out, Jet!}Jet, tôi đi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:53.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{Spike, the main gun on that\Nthing isn't fixed yet!}Spike, khẩu súng chính trên tàu\Nvẫn chưa được sửa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:29.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Nice try, buddy.}Có cố gắng đó anh bạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:56.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{What is this? Isn't this a little risky?}Cái gì đây? Có mạo hiểm quá không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:56.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{This way!}Lối này!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.83,0:17:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,{My 12 million...}Mười hai triệu của mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Hey! Are you alive?}{\i0}{\i1}Này, chị còn sống không?{\i0}
